Title: All In
Plot: A cache of missing chips from a closed down casino turn up in Vegas and a string of murders follow, leading Langston to use deadly force for the first time in his career as a CSI.
GuestStars: Liz Vassey, David Berman, Cynthia Watros, Mark Pellegrino, Andrew Rothenberg, Marc Vann, Peter Breitmayer, Sheeri Rappaport, Wayne Wilderson, Gerald McRaney
